high_descs: Turn around and go straight to the right side of the counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn left, walk forward towards the sink, then face the sink.
Cut the tomato that is in the sink.
Turn around, walk left to the white table.
Put the knife into the pan on the table.
Turn around, walk right to the sink.
Take a slice of tomato.
Turn around, walk left to the white table.
Put the slice of tomato into the pan on the table.
Take the pan from the table.
Turn right, walk to the front of the refrigerator.
Put the pan into the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a slice of tomato in it into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn backwards and walk towards the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn to the left and walk towards the sink.
Slice the red tomato in the sink with the knife.
With the knife still in the hand, turn backwards and walk towards the table on the left side.
Place the knife in the pan.
Turn backwards and turn right towards the sink.
Pick up a ,middle slice of tomato from the sink.
Turn backwards and walk towards the table on the left.
Place the slice of tomato on to the pan.
Pick up the pan from the table.
Turn right, walk towards the fridge, open the fridge with the bottle handle.
Put the pan on the top rack and close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of tomato on a pan and put it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the counter behind you
Grab the knife on the counter
Walk to the sink
Cut the tomato in the sink
Turn around, walk to the table on the left
Place the knife in the pan
Turn around, walk back to the sink
Pick up a piece of tomato
Take the slice of tomato to the table behind you on the left.
Place the tomato in the pan
Lift the pan into your hand
Turn right, walk to the fridge on your left
Open the fridge, place the tomato and pan inside.
Turn to the right, take a step, then turn right again and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife laying on the counter.
Turn to the left, take two steps, and turn to the right to face the sink.
Cut the tomato in the sink.
Turn around, take two steps, then turn left and walk forward to face a table.
Put the knife in the pan on the table.
Turn around, walk across the room, turn right, then walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the tomato slice in the sink.
Turn around, walk halfway across the room, then turn left and walk across the room to face the table.
Put the tomato in the pan on the table.
Pick up the pan with the tomato and knife in it.
Turn to the right, walk across the room, then turn to the left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pan on the top shelf, close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife, tomato slice, as well as a pan into the fridge.
